{"tid":2260133,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"粉嶺新圍軍營旁軍事禁區地盤 工人墮6米坑命危","createTime":"2020-10-27T10:48:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-27T14:46:51.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f121042f763d1421dbc8682bdd4b16b3a3267e10","tid":2260133,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T10:48:27.000Z","msg":"【18:25】年約60歲傷者姓曾，送院救治後情況危殆<br />\n<br />\n粉嶺新圍軍營旁邊一個地盤，下午3時許，一名工人疑意外墮下約6米深坑，受傷昏迷。警方及消防接報到場，由消防員將他救起，由救護車送往沙田威爾斯親王醫院搶救。警員在場調查意外原因。現場所見，地盤在軍營旁邊，地盤大閘有「軍事禁區 不得擅入」警告牌。據稱，地盤正進行打樁工程，故有多個坑洞。<br />\n<br />\n勞工處表示已知悉事件，並已派員到意外現場了解，以及就意外原因展開調查。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201027/OMJ66TJWBZBFFFZFCNMXG6IR3E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201027%2FOMJ66TJWBZBFFFZFCNMXG6IR3E%2F&d=BCqMRPjRs%2BrlYbPtDS4RDJE%2BEEUKUWA%2FtqiTfwOa%2F%2FE%3D&h=9e6763de\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201027%2FOMJ66TJWBZBFFFZFCNMXG6IR3E%2F&h=7c174837\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201027/OMJ66TJWBZBFFFZFCNMXG6IR3E/</a>"},{"pid":"fbcac0b4c05139e77dd8a07639763394a0c3af95","tid":2260133,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T10:49:30.000Z","msg":"返工 = ？？"},{"pid":"96ad62dcac9f48690f402408e41fe841d81aeb5a","tid":2260133,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T14:46:01.000Z","msg":"你還有黨呀"},{"pid":"e6f77fed164b62845f957f222b5ba2b434cc7405","tid":2260133,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fbcac0b4c05139e77dd8a07639763394a0c3af95","tid":2260133,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T10:49:30.000Z","msg":"返工 = ？？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T14:46:51.000Z","msg":"解放軍返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\